'''赫尔辛基-万塔机场'''（{{lang-fi|Helsinki-Vantaan lentoasema}}，{{lang-sv|Helsingfors-Vanda flygplats}}；[[IATA机场代码|IATA]]：'''HEL'''，[[ICAO机场代码|ICAO]]：'''EFHK'''），是[[赫尔辛基|赫尔辛基]]地区、乃至[[芬兰|芬兰]]全国最主要的机场。该机场坐落在赫尔辛基的卫星城[[万塔|万塔]]，与万塔和赫尔辛基市中心的距离分别为5公里和18公里。2019年旅客吞吐量为2186万人次<ref name="旅客数">{{cite web | url = https://www.finavia.fi/sites/default/files/documents/Passengers%20by%20Airport-fi_23.pdf | title = Passengers by airports | format = pdf | language = en | publisher = Finavia | accessdate = 2020-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200214194306/https://www.finavia.fi/sites/default/files/documents/Passengers%20by%20Airport-fi_23.pdf | archive-date = 2020-02-14 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，飞机降落次数为9.5万次<ref name="降落次数">{{cite web | url = https://www.finavia.fi/sites/default/files/documents/Landings-fi_24.pdf | title = Domestic and international air transport landings by airports | format = pdf | language = en | publisher = Finavia | accessdate = 2020-01-27 | archive-date = 2021-03-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210306163113/https://www.finavia.fi/sites/default/files/documents/Landings-fi_24.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

